Mid-sprint review:  solution for complexes in the sprint 
           sprint ususally has the dialy standups but with the time limmitatation to 30-40 minutes mostly. where we can not talk all the blockers and problems.
           so for example usually a story has 3 points intially but after starting it was added more with 6-10 points and becomes a hard blockers in some points so 
          this kind of issues will be discussed in mid sprint to achieve them.





Product grooming -define goals and prioritize the goals
Backlog Grooming
Sprint daily standups
Mid sprint review


Make sure backlog items are clear, correct, and ready for future sprints.

What happens in Backlog Refinement?
Clarify user stories
Add acceptance criteria
Break large stories into smaller tasks
Prioritize based on business value
Estimate (Story Points)
Remove outdated items---------



